<html>
<head>
<style type='text/css'>
body, td, th {
    font-family: Georgia, Times;
    font-size: 14pt;
    color: black;
    background: ivory;
}
.on_right {
    display: block;
    text-align: right;
    margin-right: 1in;
}
strong {
    font-weight: bold;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<span class="on_right">[% today.format("%A, %B %e, %Y") %]</span>
<p>
[% IF program.confnote || reg.confnote %]
<b>NOTES:</b><br>
<ul>
[% IF program.confnote %]
    [% program.confnote_br %]<br>
[% END %]
[% IF reg.confnote %]
    [% reg.confnote_br %]
[% END %]
</ul>
[% END %]
<span class="on_right">Receipt #[% reg.id %]</span>
<p>
Dear [% person.first %],
<p>
<!-- being careful of that comma before "as you requested" ... -->
We have received your deposit/payment of $[% deposit %]
and have scheduled you for<br>
[% IF personal_retreat %]
your personal retreat,
[% ELSIF program.retreat %]
    "[% program.title %]",
[% ELSE %]
    the "[% program.title %]" program[% IF program.leaders %] with [% program.leader_names %][% END %],
[% END %]
as you requested.
<p>
[% program.cl_picture %]
<p>
[% IF htdesc == 'Your Van' %]
No lodging was reserved for you since you will be staying in your own van.
[% ELSIF htdesc == 'Commuting' %]
No lodging was reserved for you since you will be commuting.
[% ELSE %]
For lodging you have been given [% article %] "[% htdesc %]" reservation.
[% END %]
<p>
[% IF reg.balance > 0 %]
    Your balance due on arrival is $[% reg.balance %] for meals,
    [% IF personal_retreat %]
		lodging and facilities.
	[% ELSE %]
	    lodging, facilities and program.
    [% END %]
    <br>
    We accept checks, money orders, Visa, MasterCard and cash.
[% ELSIF reg.balance == 0 %]
    Your account is paid in full; there is no balance due.
[% ELSIF reg.balance < 0 %]
	Because your first housing choice was not available
	you are due a refund of $[% -1*reg.balance %].
	We will issue you a refund when you check-in.
[% END %]
[% staying = (htdesc != 'Commuting') %]
[% camping = (htdesc == 'Your Tent' || htdesc == 'Center Tent') %]
<p>
We suggest that you bring the following:
<ul>
[% IF staying %]
    <li>towel (since towels are <i>not</i> provided)
    <li>alarm clock
[% END %]
<li>flashlight
<li>warm clothing for cool nights and mornings
<li>comfortable clothes and shoes for a rural setting
<li>a swimsuit for lake swimming or hot tubbing
</ul>
[% IF program.retreat %]
    <li>loose clothing suitable for breathing practices and postures
    <li>a blanket or mat for postures (optional)
[% END %]
[% IF htdesc == 'Your Tent' || htdesc == 'Center Tent' %]
    <p>
    Since you are camping remember to bring your own bedding.
    [% IF htdesc == 'Center Tent' %]
        <br>Foam mattresses are provided in center tents.
    [% END %]
[% END %]
<p>
You may wish to bring slippers, as shoes are not worn indoors.
<p>
Please <strong>DO NOT</strong> bring the following onto the property:
<ul>
<li>food
<li>drugs
<li>alcohol
<li>pets
</ul>
<strong>DO NOT</strong> wear scented body products.
<p>
Due to extreme fire precautions <strong>DO NOT</strong> bring or use incense, candles,
kerosene lamps, etc.
<p>
[% IF personal_retreat %]
Your retreat begins on the afternoon of 
[% ELSE %]
Program registration is from
[% program.reg_start %] to [% program.reg_end %] on<br>
[% END %]
[% program.sdate_obj.format("%A, %B %e") %][% IF personal_retreat %].[% ELSE %] in the Community Building.[% END %]<br>
[% IF personal_retreat && sunday %]
    Look for your housing information which will be posted
    in the Community Building lobby.
    <p>
    Dinner is served from 5:00 pm to 6:00 pm.
[% ELSE %]
	Dinner is served from
    [% IF program.retreat %]
		6:00 pm to 7:00 pm.
    [% ELSIF friday %]
		5:30 pm to 6:30 pm.
	[% ELSE %]
		5:00 pm to 6:00 pm.
	[% END %]
    <p>
	The office closes at 6:30 pm.<br>
	If you will ARRIVE LATER than 6:00 pm please call to let us know.<br>
    Notes are posted in the Community Building lobby for late arrivals.<br>
	We will save dinner for you on request.
[% END %]
<p>
[% IF ! personal_retreat %]
Your program will begin at [% program.prog_start %].<br>
[% END %]
[% IF personal_retreat %]Your retreat[% ELSE %]The program [% END %]
will end at [% program.prog_end %] on [% program.edate_obj.format("%A, %B %e") %].
<p>
[% program.canpol.policy_br %]
<p>
We look forward to seeing you here soon.
<p>
<span style="margin-left: 3in; display: block">
Sincerely,<br>
[% user.first %] [% user.last %]
</span>
<hr>
<p>
Your Charges:<br>
<ul>
<table cellpadding=3>
<tr>
<th align=right>Amount</th>
<th align=left>What</th>
</tr>
[% tot = 0 %]
[% FOR ch IN reg.charges %]
<tr>
<td align=right>[% ch.amount %]</td>
<td>[% ch.what %]</td>
</tr>
[% tot = tot + ch.amount %]
[% END %]
<tr><td align=right><span style="border-top: solid thin">[% tot %]</span></td><td>Total</td></tr>
</table>
</ul>
<p>
Your Payments:<br>
<ul>
<table cellpadding=3>
<tr>
<th align=right>Amount</th>
<th align=left>What</th>
</tr>
[% FOR p IN reg.payments %]
<tr>
<td align=right>[% p.amount %]</td>
<td>[% p.what %]</td>
</tr>
[% END %]
</table>
</ul>
</body>
</html>
